name apptools
category Package
revision 77682
shortdesc Tools for customising appendices
longdesc The package provides an \AtAppendix command to add code to a
longdesc hook that is executed when \appendix is called by the user.
longdesc Additionally, a TeX conditional \ifappendix and a LaTeX-style
longdesc conditional \IfAppendix are provided to check if \appendix has
longdesc already been called.
